      "title": "Scholarship December 04 - Date December 05",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Dates for Grade 5 Scholarship Examination and General Certificate of Studies A Level Examination to be held in 2022 have been announced.",
        "Accordingly, the grade 5 scholarship exam is scheduled to begin on December 04th and the advanced level exam is scheduled to begin on December 05th."
